'''基思·克里斯托弗·羅利博士'''（{{lang-en|Dr. Keith Christopher Rowley}}；{{bd|1949年|10月24日|}}），是一名[[千里達及托巴哥|千里達及托巴哥]]與政治人物。

他在1991年進入{{le|千里達及托巴哥眾議院|House of Representatives (Trinidad and Tobago)}}擔任西迭戈馬丁選區議員<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ttparliament.org/members.php?mid=54&id=KRO01 |title=Current Members of the House of Representatives > The Honourable Dr. Keith Rowley, MP |publisher=Parliament of Trinidad and Tobago |date= |accessdate=25 June 2010 |archive-date=2015-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001170656/http://www.ttparliament.org/members.php?mid=54&id=KRO01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2010年起成為[[人民民族运动|人民民族运动]] 黨魁，同時為{{le|反對黨領袖 (千里達及托巴哥)|Leader of the Opposition (Trinidad and Tobago)|千里達及托巴哥議會的反對黨領袖}}。

{{le|2015年千里達及托巴哥大選|Trinidad and Tobago general election, 2015|2015年選舉中}}，人民民族運動取得眾議院41席中23席成為議會最大黨，羅利於2015年9月9日由[[千里達及托巴哥總統|總統]][[安東尼·卡莫納|安東尼·卡莫納]]任命，宣誓就任[[千里達及托巴哥總理|千里達及托巴哥總理]]<ref>Linda Hutchinson-Jafar, [http://ca.reuters.com/article/topNews/idCAKCN0R92JS20150909 "Trinidad's new prime minister, Keith Rowley, sworn in"] {{Wayback|url=http://ca.reuters.com/article/topNews/idCAKCN0R92JS20150909 |date=20150913033445 }}, Reuters Canada, 9 September 2015.</ref><ref>[http://www.stabroeknews.com/2015/news/stories/09/09/rowley-sworn-in-as-tt-pm/ "Rowley sworn in as T&T PM"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.stabroeknews.com/2015/news/stories/09/09/rowley-sworn-in-as-tt-pm/ |date=20160819061215 }}, ''Stabroek News'', 9 September 2015.</ref>。人民民族運動在2020年大選取得眾議院22席，繼續保持執政權<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.voanews.com/americas/trinidad-and-tobago-prime-minister-begins-second-term-following-election-result-challenges |title=Trinidad And Tobago Prime Minister Begins Second Term Following Election Result Challenges |publisher=VOA |date=2020-08-20 |accessdate=2020-08-24 |archive-date=2020-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919095428/https://www.voanews.com/americas/trinidad-and-tobago-prime-minister-begins-second-term-following-election-result-challenges |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

